f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得乾淨d就無事</blockquote><br />\n自己吊同被人吊又點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會有掙扎痕跡</blockquote><br />\n比人打暈先吊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9c8018f0ca440df1ceb99c883d1b7c1d705688","tid":241330,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>在說明這一理論之前，先說說勒頸的死因和吊頸的死因不同之處。前者是以氣管被堵塞造成的窒息為多，後者以輸往腦部的血液被堵斷所造成的腦內缺氧而死的占大多數。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得乾淨d就無事</blockquote><br />\n自己吊同被人吊又點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力度唔同？</blockquote><br />\n被人吊會掙扎 傷口唔同 暈咗先吊就冇唔同"},{"pid":"9ccc20cf130b41ddad84f600b0387ba24630c75c","tid":241330,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"向腦部供血的動脈有兩種，頸動脈和在脊椎旁邊被骨頭保護著的椎動脈。勒脖子的方式，即使頸動脈被堵住，但被骨頭保護的椎骨動脈是堵不住的，但上吊的方式，脖子被斜上方吊起形成了角度，因此內外同時堵死，向腦部的供血剎那間就停止了。&nbsp;<br />\n兩者的差異從屍體上即可明瞭。勒頸的屍體由椎骨動脈向腦部的供血雖繼續不斷，但相反地由腦部輸送血液的頸動脈卻被堵塞了，因此變成紫色而瘀血; 上吊的方式則不見瘀血。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘀血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b09735fb0bc8a849566fb6d266d88856a14f1ab","tid":241330,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e38a4dd6d54d049c5e8f18130cd36add7a4445d","tid":241330,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係自殺就直接講啦 有咩好調查<br />\n點自殺又唔講 擺明被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑警</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為自殺同被殺係兩樣野，係驗得出<br />\n<br />\n佢依家唔講</blockquote><br />\n點會同你講係被自殺阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪傻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1262f9fa098dd8051069da254a6620c6a064e75a","tid":241330,"uid":115217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1.捉返黎<br />\n2.錄口供<br />\n3.打犯，犯人掙扎<br />\n4.犯死左<br />\n5.個犯行到邊，cctv壞到邊<br />\n6.打死犯太大劑，屈佢自殺先<br />\n7.毅進仔合力吊佢上消防頭，點知一下就爆左<br />\n8.換倉<br />\n9.諗唔到野，直接話個犯吊頸死<br />\n10.個犯識用usb綁人，用usb自殺好合理，放風<br />\n11.呀頭表示入倉前有搜身架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊會有usb線<br />\n12.個話犯係錄口供個時神偷上身整條lan線上身<br />\n13.放風，個犯偷左條lan線用黎自殺<br />\n14.因為無lan線無得上網，錄口供個時cctv廢左<br />\n15.驚察知道cctv廢左之後即搵it狗黎整cctv<br />\n16. it狗唔知做乜，整壞哂所有cctv。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af06a110ae4a7f1e55a2490881230c4c84af4e3","tid":241330,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1.捉返黎<br />\n2.錄口供<br />\n3.打犯，犯人掙扎<br />\n4.犯死左<br />\n5.個犯行到邊，cctv壞到邊<br />\n6.打死犯太大劑，屈佢自殺先<br />\n7.毅進仔合力吊佢上消防頭，點知一下就爆左<br />\n8.換倉<br />\n9.諗唔到野，直接話個犯吊頸死<br />\n10.個犯識用usb綁人，用usb自殺好合理，放風<br />\n11.呀頭表示入倉前有搜身架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊會有usb線<br />\n12.個話犯係錄口供個時神偷上身整條lan線上身<br />\n13.放風，個犯偷左條lan線用黎自殺<br />\n14.因為無lan線無得上網，錄口供個時cctv廢左<br />\n15.驚察知道cctv廢左之後即搵it狗黎整cctv<br />\n16. it狗唔知做乜，整壞哂所有cctv。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" cl